glosses: to be proud, to be arrogant

examples.translation: Everyone can do this don't be arrogant

glosses: to see oneself higher than someone else, to be arrogant (towards)

examples.text: Bir de utanmaz utanmaz bana büyüklendi
examples.translation: On top of that he also shamelessly saw himself over me

glosses: to be arrogantly offensive towards, to be arrogantly rude towards

examples.translation: You can't be arrogantly rude towards your parents like this!
